      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are proud to present this extraordinary vehicle, preserved in impeccable showroom condition. This specimen represents the pinnacle of its class, having been maintained to the highest standards with no compromise on care or mechanical integrity. Every surface, from the flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior appointments, reflects a level of preservation rarely seen on the market. For the discerning buyer who demands unrivaled quality and a turn-key ownership experience, this vehicle stands as a testament to automotive excellence.",
