    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this beauty in person. It\u2019s in absolute showroom condition\u2014not a single scratch or speck of dust to be found! I\u2019ve babied this car from day one, and it still has that wonderful new-car smell and drives like a total dream. If you\u2019re looking for a ride that\u2019s basically perfect but without the brand-new sticker price, this is the one for you. Come grab the keys and take it for a spin!",
      "price": 46500.0,
