    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Presenting an absolute masterpiece of automotive preservation. This vehicle is in showroom condition, having been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled garage since day one. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish thanks to a professional ceramic coating, with absolutely zero chips, swirls, or imperfections in the paintwork. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium hand-stitched leather still carries that distinct new-car aroma, and every surface\u2014from the brushed aluminum accents to the high-definition glass displays\u2014is entirely flawless. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, featuring a comprehensive service history documented exclusively through authorized dealerships. It has never seen rain, let alone snow, and has been driven only on fair-weather weekends to ensure its integrity. This is a rare opportunity to own a pristine example of engineering excellence that looks, feels, and drives exactly as it did the day it rolled off the assembly line.",
      "price": 48900.0,
